<br>
I'm sure that many of the members of SS come accross to strangers as nice people.  They are when they have something to gain.  Dolus and Kausak come across as very intelligent and verbose individuals with their few posts on EQVault.  Yet, in person if they know where you stand they can be quite rude.  Still in my opinion you should follow your own conscience on this.  For myself I'm done with it.  I'm tired of it.  I'm not a fan of karma or fate, but you do reap what you sow.  I dont, and have never, advocated more than a silent boycott of SS.  Anything more is counter productive.  Just ignore them and eventually they're get tired of the lack of attention and move to Sullon Zek where they can get more attention by camping people's bind spots.<br>
